column16: Leury Garcia pops out to shortstop Mike Aviles.
Gordon Beckham flies out to left fielder Jason Kubel.
Alejandro De Aza pops out to third baseman Lonnie Chisenhall in foul territory.
Marcus Semien singles on a ground ball to third baseman Lonnie Chisenhall.   Miguel Gonzalez to 2nd.
Miguel Gonzalez singles on a soft fly ball to center fielder Drew Stubbs.
Dayan Viciedo grounds out, shortstop Mike Aviles to first baseman Nick Swisher.
Avisail Garcia pops out to second baseman Jose Ramirez.
Conor Gillaspie grounds into a force out, second baseman Jose Ramirez to shortstop Mike Aviles.   Jeff Keppinger out at 2nd.    Conor Gillaspie to 1st.
Jeff Keppinger reaches on catcher interference by Kelly Shoppach.    Jeff Keppinger to 1st.
